headline: Is Hewlett Packard Enterprise Stock Outperforming the S&P 500?

headline: HPE to Webcast HPE Securities Analyst Meeting 2025
summary: HOUSTON, September 17, 2025--HPE (NYSE: HPE) will host its Securities Analyst Meeting on October 15, 2025. Join a live webcast to hear featured presentations from Antonio Neri, president and CEO; Marie Myers, executive vice president and CFO; and Rami Rahim, executive vice president, president and general manager, HPE Networking, as they review the company's strategy and long-term financial outlook.

headline: DRUID AI Raises $31 Million Series C to Accelerate Agentic AI Platform Growth Under New CEO Joseph Kim
summary: DRUID AI today announced it has secured $31 million in Series C financing to advance the global expansion of its enterprise-ready agentic AI platform under the leadership of its new CEO Joseph Kim. The strategic investment was led by Cipio Partners, with participation from TQ Ventures, Karma Ventures, Smedvig, and Hoxton Ventures.
